{"id":54,"title":"问：如果让你设计一个缓存系统，需要支持根据最近最少使用策略淘汰数据（即LRU缓存），你会如何实现？","slug":"问：如果让你设计一个缓存系统，需要支持根据最近最少使用策略淘汰数据（即LRU缓存），你会如何实现？-1766595050","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：LRU（Least Recently Used）缓存可以用哈希表+双向链表**来实现。哈希表用于根据键快速定位缓存项，双向链表按访问时间从新到旧排列节点：每当访问或插入数据时，将对应节点移到链表头部；当缓存满需淘汰时，移除链表尾部节点（即最久未使用的数据）。具体来说，可维护一个双向链表存储键值对节点，最近使用的节点移动到表头；同时用一个哈希表将键映射到对应的链表节点，以在O(1)时间内完成查找和更新。这样既能快速访问，又能根据访问历史淘汰最久未使用的数据。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.843054+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.843054+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-8092-9a5c-eec6bbfbd1a5","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":54,"blog_post_id":54,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.607266+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.607266+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.843054+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:50.843054+08:00"}